# Intuition
Divide the RANGE INTO 3 PARTS INSTEAD OF 2
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Instead of doing Binary search we are dividing the range into 3 parts , which will minimise the fuction calls . 
we have two mid points m1 and m2 . and we obtain the result by using them (See the code) .


# Complexity
- Time complexity: log(N) base 3 
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: O(1)
